---
// Component Imports
import Layout from "../layouts/PageLayout.astro";
import Hero from "../layouts/WorkHero.astro";
import mangesh from "../images/mangesh.png";
import mangeshFull from "../images/mangesh-lg.png";
import Modal from "../components/modal.astro";

const meta = {
  title: "Mangesh Thombare",
  description: "Portfolio website for a game designer.",
};
---

<Layout {meta}>
  <Hero />
  <div id="content-wrapper" class="md: mt-40 lg:mt-0 2xl:mt-80 container p-8 mx-auto lg:p-24 dark:bg-dark-900 dark:text-white">
    <div class="container min-h-full px-4 my-2 space-y-5 leading-relaxed text-left lg:px-8">
      <div id="pagination" class="flex flex-wrap items-center space-x-4">
        <a href="/" class="hover:duration-200 hover:transition-all hover:ease hover:text-geraldine-500 focus:border-b-4 focus:outline-none focus:border-geraldine-500">Home</a>
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" aria-label="arrow">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 5l7 7-7 7M5 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
        </svg>
        <a href="/work#content-wrapper" class="hover:duration-200 hover:transition-all hover:ease hover:text-geraldine-500 focus:border-b-4 focus:outline-none focus:border-geraldine-500">Work</a>
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" aria-label="arrow">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 5l7 7-7 7M5 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
        </svg>
        <a href="#" class="focus:border-b-4 focus:outline-none focus:border-geraldine-500">Mangesh Thombare</a>
      </div>

      <div class="my-6 text-3xl font-semibold font-display">
        Mangesh
        <span class="text-cyan-600 dark:text-cyan-300">Thombare</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col items-start md:flex-row">
        <div class="flex flex-shrink-0 mx-2 my-4 border-2 border-gray-200 shadow-lg dark:border-gray-800 md:w-1/2 lg:w-auto hover:border-geraldine-400 dark:hover:border-geraldine-400">
          <img class="object-contain w-full h-auto dark:filter dark:brightness-75 dark:contrast-125" src={mangesh} alt="Mangesh Thombare" />
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col px-2 mb-8 space-y-3 md:pl-6">
          <p>This was a portfolio website project for a game designer. His requirements were a responsive website which showcased his CV, embedded videos and documents of his completed projects and lastly a contact form.</p>

          <ul class="list-decimal list-inside">
            <li>Portfolio website.</li>
            <li>Responsive design.</li>
            <li>Embedded videos and documents.</li>
            <li>Modal for images.</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <div>
              <a id="modal3-trigger" class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white dark:text-dark-700 transition-all duration-150 rounded-md shadow-md cursor-pointer ease bg-emerald-600 hover:bg-emerald-500 focus:ring-4 focus:outline-none focus:ring-emerald-400 dark:bg-emerald-400 dark:hover:bg-emerald-500 dark:focus:ring-emerald-200" tabindex="0">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-current" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" aria-label="Image">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 16l4.586-4.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L16 16m-2-2l1.586-1.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L20 14m-6-6h.01M6 20h12a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
                </svg>
                <span>Screenshot</span>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex py-10">
        <div class="flex items-start">
          <svg class="inline-block w-5 h-5 fill-current text-geraldine-600 md:w-10 md:h-10" aria-label="Quotes" viewBox="0 0 512 512">
            <path d="M464 256h-80v-64c0-35.3 28.7-64 64-64h8c13.3 0 24-10.7 24-24V56c0-13.3-10.7-24-24-24h-8c-88.4 0-160 71.6-160 160v240c0 26.5 21.5 48 48 48h128c26.5 0 48-21.5 48-48V304c0-26.5-21.5-48-48-48zm-288 0H96v-64c0-35.3 28.7-64 64-64h8c13.3 0 24-10.7 24-24V56c0-13.3-10.7-24-24-24h-8C71.6 32 0 103.6 0 192v240c0 26.5 21.5 48 48 48h128c26.5 0 48-21.5 48-48V304c0-26.5-21.5-48-48-48z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="px-4 space-y-3 md:px-8">
          <p>Akshay designed my portfolio website. The best part about working with him was that, I got a site fully customized and tailored to my needs. It is easy to navigate and works seamlessly on all platforms mobiles, tablets or PCs. When certain changes had to be made, they were delivered with precision within 24 hours of request. He has the patience to work at your pace every step of the way. You can have a fully personalized experience at an affordable price. It has been a pleasure working with Akshay.</p>

          <p class="font-semibold text-right">- Mangesh Thombare</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-end">
          <svg class="inline-block w-5 h-5 fill-current text-geraldine-600 md:w-10 md:h-10" aria-label="Quotes" viewBox="0 0 512 512">
            <path d="M464 32H336c-26.5 0-48 21.5-48 48v128c0 26.5 21.5 48 48 48h80v64c0 35.3-28.7 64-64 64h-8c-13.3 0-24 10.7-24 24v48c0 13.3 10.7 24 24 24h8c88.4 0 160-71.6 160-160V80c0-26.5-21.5-48-48-48zm-288 0H48C21.5 32 0 53.5 0 80v128c0 26.5 21.5 48 48 48h80v64c0 35.3-28.7 64-64 64h-8c-13.3 0-24 10.7-24 24v48c0 13.3 10.7 24 24 24h8c88.4 0 160-71.6 160-160V80c0-26.5-21.5-48-48-48z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <Modal triggerId="modal3-trigger" title="Mangesh Thombare">
    <div class="mt-3 text-center">
      <img class="dark:filter dark:brightness-75 dark:contrast-125" src={mangeshFull} alt="Mangesh Thombare Full Image" />
    </div>
  </Modal>
</Layout>
